Installation instructions for openBibleViewer 0.8:
---------------------------

openBibleViewer requires:

- Qt-devel >= 4.6
  or libqt-devel >= 4.6
- cmake
- clucene >= 2.3.3.4
- quazip >= 0.4.3
- zlib

Resolve Dependecies on openSUSE 12.2:
----------------------
__sudo zypper in libquazip1 quazip-devel zlib zlib-devel libqt-devel automoc4 cmake libclucene2 clucene-core-devel__

sudo apt install libquazip1 libquazip-dev zlib1g-dev libclucene-dev automoc cmake lzma pkg-config qtbase5-dev qtscript5-dev


Compile openBibleViewer from git:
----------------------------------
git clone git://github.com/metaxy/openBibleViewer.git
cd openBibleViewer
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX='/usr' ..
make
sudo make install

Compile openBibleViewer:
---------------------------

tar -xjf openBibleViewer-0.8.tar.bz2
cd ~/openBibleViewer-0.8
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX='/usr' ..
make
sudo make install

